         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Melbourne bot Garden ¶ 14/11/70. ¶  ¶ Would you be so kind to tell me, dear Mr Clarke, whether Mr Hoffmann can get his remuneration for Sept and October. ¶  If so he will call for it in the morning at...</supplied>
            </head>
            <ab rend="number"
                style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: -1in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
                type="heading">70.11.14</ab>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To Marcus Clarke</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">VPRS 5834/P0/1, inward correspondence p. 64, VA 1411 Industrial and Technological Museum, Public Record Office, Victoria.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>MS annotation: 'R. private note <seg style="">
                        <hi rend="underline">Committee meet tomorrow</hi>
                     </seg> 14th Nov. Rec. 15th Nov. 1870.' See M to M. Clarke, 15 November 1870.</p>
               </note>Melbourne bot Garden</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">14/11/70.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Would you be so kind to tell me, dear Mr Clarke, whether Mr Hoffmann can get his remuneration for Sept and October.<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>See M to […], November 1870 (in this edition as 70-11-00e), and M. Clarke to M, 17 November 1870 (in this edition as 70-11-17b).</p>
               </note> If so he will call for it in the morning at your Office.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">With best regards</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller.</p>
         </div>
      </body>
